{"type": "article", "id": 2488, "title": "Apple Watch 充电底座", "description": "", "date": "2014-09-22T08:38:30Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 7, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606052325118Npx1FdTKI0ODsvg.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t在 Apple Watch 正式发布后，来自旧金山的数码配件品牌 DODOcase 抢先登陆这个蕴含巨大商机的领域，为 Apple Watch 打造了一款专属充电底座，采用精选木材构成底座部分，使用时用户只需将 Apple Watch 放在底座上即可，因为 Apple Watch 本身采用的就是 MagSafe 吸磁方式进行充电。这款产品预计将在 2015 年正式面世，建议零售价为 60-80 美元。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232509fUY3oKmzGslhOLpR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6609375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232510ZDVPRjk16u85CLpq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6609375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232510H689NwgyLOGDuJaW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6609375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}